{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_07_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 水が垂れてるいい男？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "――それでね、その時すずにゃんが\n寝ぼけたまま芽衣を見てこう言ったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So‚ you know‚ that's when Suzu-nyan\nlooked at Mei while still half-asleep and said this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "「うぅ～ん……お母様ぁ……\nおしりペンペンは勘弁してくださいまし～」だって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Uuuh… Mother…\nPlease spare me from the spanking~\" she said!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すずらしいな……ん？　電話か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's so like Suzu… Hm? A call?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.800000159,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 943.3333333,
          "startTime": 18.7433334923
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666507700002,
          "startTime": 22.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お母さんだ。ごめんね、ちょっといい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it's my mom. Sorry‚ can you give me a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8666686058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　うん、うん、大丈夫だよ\n今{user}さんとお話してた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Yeah‚ yeah‚ I'm fine.\nI'm talking with {user}-san right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.86666797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、うん……え？\nえーーーーーー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah… What?\nWhaaaat!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333346367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "うん……分かった。また電話するね。それじゃ\n……えっとね、お父さんが入院しちゃったみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… Got it. I'll call again later. Bye.\n…So‚ it seems like my dad was admitted to the hospital.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.56666797,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5336.666030899998,
          "startTime": 47.33666797
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "入院！？　大変だ、今すぐにでも向かう準備をしないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Admitted!? That's serious‚ we need to prepare to go immediately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0000019391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　いいよいいよ！\nそんな大した感じじゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? No‚ no‚ it's fine!\nIt's not that big of a deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7000005405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんだ。入院なんて大事じゃないか\nどこの病院かは聞いたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? Being admitted is serious.\nDid you hear which hospital he's in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0000005405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あー、いやー、ほんと、うん\nそこまで急がなくても大丈夫っていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ well‚ it's really‚ um…\nIt's not that urgent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1000005405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね……ぎっくり腰になっちゃったんだ、お父さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ uh… My dad threw out his back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3666678429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　ぎっくり腰？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What? Threw out his back?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6000011762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "本を詰めた段ボールをね「これくらいなんともない」\nなんて言って持ち上げたら、こう、グキッ！　って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He tried to lift a box full of books saying‚ \"This is nothing‚\"\nAnd then‚ like‚ snap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4666672071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんも「だから無理しないでって言ったのに」って\n呆れてたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My mom was like‚ \"I told you not to push yourself.\"\nShe was sighing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……でも、お父さんからすれば\n大変なのは違いないよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… But it's still serious\nfor your dad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8000005405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "うん。早めにお見舞いに行きたいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I want to visit him soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.0333345096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、スケジュールを調整するから\n早めに顔を見せに行ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. I'll adjust the schedule‚\nSo you can go see him soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8666672071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ありがとう！\nまったくもう、お父さんてばドジだなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san!\nSeriously‚ my dad is so clumsy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9666672071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後の仕事終わり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later‚ after work",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8000010174,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1839.9999618999914,
          "startTime": 129.6400009793
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "わー！　すっごい雨！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! It's raining so hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4333406131,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 130.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "予報より早かったな……傘を持ち歩いてなくてすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's earlier than the forecast… Sorry‚ I didn't bring an umbrella.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8666739464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.1333406131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないでいいよー。ほんといきなりだったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it. It really came out of nowhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1333406131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3000072797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、もし{user}さんが\n傘を持ってたら……相合傘になってたのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… But if {user}-san\nhad an umbrella… Would we be sharing it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9666672071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういう時はちゃんと二本持ってくるから大丈夫だ\nほら、このタオルで拭いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would make sure to bring two umbrellas in that case.\nHere‚ use this towel to dry off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7333338738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.4000072797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "わー、ありがと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ thanks!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4000072797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも早く拭きなよ……って\nむむ？　むむむ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should dry off too‚ {user}-san… Wait\nHmm? Hmmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8666672071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.2666739464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_01-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、髪の毛が濡れてて\nいつもと雰囲気違うかも？　ドキッてしちゃった！",
      "translations": {
